If your domain is hosted at OVH, please create the A record by selecting the relevant domain name, the "Advanced mode" -> "DNS zone" -> "Add an entry". Enter:
Type of record: A
Sub-domain: {0}
Target: {1}
If your domain is hosted elsewhere, create the A record on this domain via the manager of your provider, using the above information.

If your domain is hosted at OVH, please create the AAAA record by selecting the relevant domain name, the "Advanced mode" -> "DNS zone" -> "Add an entry". Enter:
Type of record: AAAA
Sub-domain: {0}
Target: {1}
If your domain is hosted elsewhere, create the AAAA record on this domain via the manager of your provider, using the above information.

Priority: {0}; target: {1}
Priority: {2}; target: {3}
Priority: {4}; target: {5}
Priority: {6}; target: {7}
